      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "I don't generally write code nor plan on it. I sometimes read PRs, but not often.\n\nMy team vibecoded a quarterly planning tool while I was out and now I need to maintain it, so now I have to vibecode some. Honestly, it's terribly designed from a UX and data model perspective because they rushed it out to replace the Google Sheets we'd been using previously",
